title: 2022 CFB Pick Em Week 7
description:
El Pres, Big Cat & Rico are back for Week 7 of the CFB season. After the blowout on DPS last night, this episode is a bit of a therapy session for Rico. The whole crew talks through several pressing issues to all get onto the same page.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
